    "name": "Task Invoicing API Demo - Valid Requests Only",
    "description": "Valid demo flow for the invoice API. Create an invoice, manually set invoice_id, view it, update it, send it, simulate delivered notification webhook, then verify the invoice status.\n\nNote: POST /api/invoices returns 201 with an empty JSON object {} and does not return the created invoice_id. Manually set the collection variable `invoice_id` before running requests that require it.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "8551187"
  },
